<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #333;">About the Project 📂</h1>
        
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
            Welcome to your personal <strong>Travel Bucket List</strong>! 🌍 <br><br>
            This platform is designed for travelers who want to keep track of their dream destinations in one place. Whether it's a beach in Maldives or a trek in the Himalayas, you can save them all here.
        </p>
        
        <div style="margin: 30px 0; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; text-align: left;">
            <strong style="color: #d9534f;">What you can do:</strong>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 2;">
                <li>*Add* new places you want to visit.</li>
                <li>*Upload* beautiful photo of your destinations.</li>
                <li>*Edit* details as your plans change.</li>
                <li>*Remove* places once you've crossed them off your list.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="font-style: italic; color: #888;">"To travel is to live." - Start building your list today!</p>

        <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="/" class="back-btn" style="text-decoration: none; background-color: #d9534f; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">← Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>